        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Chicago&#44;</placeName>
                <date>February 24&#44; 1862</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser&#44;</addressee>
                <placeName>Philadelphia.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Dear sir&#44;</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">You conduct your paper always in such a
                <lb/>
 fair manner that I suppose&#44; I shall
                not ask in
                <lb/>
 vain to do me the favor of granting some space&#44; in
                <lb/>
 the next
                number of the Occident&#44; to the enclosed card.
                <lb/>
 Think what ever you may of my
                religious views &#38;c. I
                <lb/>
 shall noll
                <add>&#63;</add> and will not say anything
                against your
                <lb/>
 regarding these views erroneous&#44; if you only consider
                <lb/>
                them honestly conceived and entertained. But&#44; I
                <lb/>
 pray you&#44; do not class
                me with those vainglorious
                <lb/>
 braggarts who style themselves Doctors&#44;
                Professors&#44;
                <lb/>
 Reverends &#38;c. without blushing&#44; and who&#44;
                without
                <lb/>
 the least reluctance&#44; publicly speak of their own
                <lb/>
 selves as
                the pillars of Judaism and the champion
                <lb/>
 of Israel. The saying of Nittai the
                Arbelite
                <add>Hebrew</add>
                <lb/>
 is a very good maxim&#44; and&#44; therefore&#44; I dislike
                it
                <lb/>
 in the highest degree to have even my name mentioned
                <lb/>
 in one and the
                same class with those pretentious
                <lb/>
 impostors of which there are too many in
                <placeName>America.</placeName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Accept&#44; rev
                <hi rend="sup">d</hi>
                <hi rend="sub">.</hi> sir&#44; the assurance of my high
                estimation
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Very resp&#39;fully&#44; yours</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">
                <persName role="author">B. Felsenthal.</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
